task.summary: Added null checking to Bootstrapper to prevent errors. This makes it so that you can have the Core Framework in your project and not be forced to use the bootstrapper
Default the Start Scene and Boot Scene to be null if there is no Settings Scritable Object
Documentation Updated Vector(2)(3)(4) added Range Extension
Added OrNull to fix some NullReferenceExceptions when a GameObject is slated to be destroyed.
Added some useful Transformation extensions and their equivalents to Game Object.
